                                                                                                          rdfs:comment "BPMN Data Store - persistent information repository accessed by UserTasks during the certificate of employment process." ;
                                                                                                          rdfs:label "Data Stores" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/obrienchrist/ontologies/2026/5/Certificate-of-Employment-Ontology/EndEvent
<http://www.semanticweb.org/obrienchrist/ontologies/2026/5/Certificate-of-Employment-Ontology/EndEvent> rdf:type owl:Class ;
